Template: vaulthalla/init-db
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Initialize a PostgreSQL database for Vaulthalla?
 Vaulthalla requires a PostgreSQL database. If enabled, the installer will
 attempt to create a database and user on the configured PostgreSQL server.
 .
 If disabled, you must create the required database and user manually.
 See /usr/share/doc/vaulthalla/README.Debian for instructions.

Template: vaulthalla/superadmin-uid
Type: string
Default: auto
Description: Linux UID to assign as super-admin (leave empty to auto-detect)
 The super-admin account is mapped to a Linux user for privileged operations.
 Enter a numeric UID, or leave as 'auto' to detect the installing user.
 The UID will be assigned once and not modified automatically thereafter.
